To use luaposix in your lua programs you must set this environ variable:

   LUA_INIT = "loadlib('${PREFIX}/lib/libluaposix.so','luaopen_posix')();"

The rest of luaposix is installed in:

   ${PREFIX}/lib/lua/

===========================================================================
